column5: A friend is looking to buy a 15' extension for his transducer cable as he is mounting a Mark IV HDI on his pontoon boat. Lowrance Canada only gave him the Navico phone number. Radio world has them on the website but are out of stock for 3-4 weeks. Any ideas?
Try Jos @ angling outfitters in Woodstock. He may have what your looking for.  G

Maybe Boaters World would have it.  https://www.google.ca/url?sa=t&rct=j&q=&esrc=s&source=web&cd=2&cad=rja&uact=8&ved=0CC4QFjABahUKEwjtk8ze1v7GAhVTFpIKHRwNBBE&url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.boatersworld.com%2F&ei=vee3Va3BHdOsyAScmpCIAQ&usg=AFQjCNGcFRAntGanJEDjfu1D4W3RNFBUdw&bvm=bv.98717601,d.aWw
Had lebarons come through for me when radioworld is put of stock
